displayName: Golden City Dromos Underground Arena Reception

parameters:
Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: Without delay, I would like all of you
to defeat the reigning champion of the underground arena.
Clea: The reigning champion, you say?

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: It is a monster that suddenly appeared
a few months ago and is feared as the Iron Mask here.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: The audience gathers out of curiosity
to see something scary... but unfortunately, it is too
strong and no bets have been placed.

Clea: Understood. If we can win, will you help us with our
search for people?

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: We can't afford to be complacent, but
let's cooperate despite the trouble it may bring.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: In return, I ask that you defeat the
Iron Mask.
Fuego with the hawk's eye, Please give me the iron mask.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: It seems my luck hasn't abandoned me
if all of you have come.
Clea: Please provide us with the details of the request.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: Although there are illegal
organizations in various places, we have established our own
rules and operate within them.

Priestess Sophia: Is this request related to someone who has
broken those rules?

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: That's correct. We have confirmed the
existence of a group engaged in illegal gambling.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: Most of them are former thieves, and
they engage in scams rather than gambling.

Clea: Why did you choose to request our help in Valier
instead of Oros?

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: We have similar requests throughout
the empire to restrain their activities, of course...

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: I was hoping that all of you would
come.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: This request is to completely destroy
a large-scale gambling establishment, specifically to
capture a man named Lance, who is the ringleader.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: Also, this is optional, but there is a
small job here.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: I will also accompany you. For any
optional tasks, I will provide additional compensation
separately.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: The boss of the Dojo was a man of
integrity. It's a shame we lost such a skilled gambler.

Underground Arena Receptionist: The regular arena is
currently closed. Our customers have come to see the
absolute champion, you know.

Underground arena receptionist: Do you want to challenge the
absolute champion?
Clea (Let's prepare first and then do it)

Underground arena receptionist: Everyone, please challenge
the absolute champion together.

Clea: Is it all of us? Does that mean there are multiple
Iron Masks?

Underground arena receptionist: Even with a 4 vs 1, it's not
a bet. This is the absolute champion of the underground
arena.

Underground arena receptionist: I'm looking forward to
everyone's battles.

Underground Arena Receptionist: The regular arena is
currently closed. Our customers have come to see the
absolute champion, you know.

Underground Arena Receptionist: Welcome to the Underground
Arena. Who will be participating today?
Receptionist: Here is the next list. Is it alright?
Clea: Well then, I'll be going.
Thief Nora: I have a bad feeling... Please be careful!
Mage Relm: I'll show you my genius talent!

Priestess Sophia: You mustn't let your guard down... Be
careful.
Thief Nora: I-I'm scared, but I'll do my best!
Clea: Please protect your life above all else.

Priestess Sophia: I'll be going now, to have a drink before
the match...
Mage Relm: Are you really going to be okay...?

Underground Arena Receptionist: We look forward to your next
challenge.

Nobleman: Welcome to the world of darkness! Here, you can
recall the twisted pleasure of the battlefield.

The woman with bloodshot eyes: Humans killing each other in
earnest... hehe... Is there any greater form of
entertainment?

Pitiful Man: She was a fortune teller, but she saw too much
of people's futures and ended up going crazy.
Clea: We managed to win somehow.
Thief Nora: I'm glad we were able to come back safely~!
Mage Relm: Hehe, this is the true power of a genius!

Priestess Sophia: I was so worried that I almost finished
the wine.
Thief Nora: I was so scared...
Clea: I'm glad Nora-san is safe above all else.

Priestess Sophia: They were all terrifying opponents... Oh,
my wine is empty.

Mage Relm: It's surprising that you were drinking during the
match...

Greedy Merchant: The secret to business is never misjudging
the value.

Greedy Merchant: To think there's a goddess in this filthy
place...! Your beauty is worth paying something for.

Greedy Merchant: Take this and... you should leave this
dangerous place.

Greedy Merchant: This isn't a place for beautiful women, you
know?

Underground Arena Shop Clerk: The shop is currently closed.
I'm going to see the Iron Mask too, you know.

Underground Arena Shop Clerk: Hello there, miss. Would you
like to exchange something?
Underground Arena Shop Clerk: Here you go.
Underground Arena Shop Clerk: Here you go.
Underground Arena Shop Clerk: Here you go.
Ring of the Berserker, 10,000 pieces en(v[92] >= 10000)
Ring of the Magic Fanatic, 10,000 pieces en(v[92] >= 10000)

Underground Arena Shop Clerk: Is there anything else you
need?
Do you want to skip the adult scene?

Fuego, the Hawk's Eye: Please infiltrate the illegal
gambling den and buy us some time, regardless of the method.

Fuego, the Hawk's Eye: Then allow me to guide you to the
location of the illegal gambling den.
